You can simply ask Alexa to control your smart products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our “WOW SOLUTION” app in app market then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in “WOW SOLUTION” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable “WOW SOLUTION” skill, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the light.
Alexa, turn off the light.
Alexa, set the light to 50%.
Alexa, set light to green.
Alexa, lock the WOW lock.
Alexa, unlock the WOW lock.
Alexa, show me the camera.
